            <history-note id="DLM325801"><amended-provision>Section 7B(1A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 December 2002</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM162681">section 9(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Takeovers Amendment Act 2002</amending-leg> (2002 No 45).</history-note>
