              <history-note id="DLM2587010"><amended-provision>Section 35(1)(b)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>24 November 2009</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM2498696">section 23(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Securities Markets Amendment Act 2009</amending-leg> (2009 No 54).</history-note>
