              <history-note id="DLM3100615"><amended-provision>Section 35(1)(c)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>7 July 2010</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM3044621">section 16(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Takeovers Amendment Act 2010</amending-leg> (2010 No 88).</history-note>
              <history-note id="DLM3100616"><amended-provision>Section 35(1)(d)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>7 July 2010</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM3044621">section 16(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Takeovers Amendment Act 2010</amending-leg> (2010 No 88).</history-note>
