              <history-note id="DLM326363"><amended-provision>Section 39</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>repealed</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 October 2006</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM384577">section 20</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Takeovers Amendment Act 2006</amending-leg> (2006 No 48).</history-note>
