          <para>
            <text>This is an eprint of the Takeovers Act 1993. The eprint incorporates all the amendments to the Act as at 7 July 2010. The list of amendments at the end of these notes specifies all the amendments incorporated into this eprint since 3 September 2007.</text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Relevant provisions of any amending enactments that contain transitional, savings, or application provisions that cannot be compiled in the eprint are also included, after the principal enactment, in chronological order.</text>
